SST 两方程模型
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "YanChao_2020"
literal "false"

\end_inset

：SST 模型是目前广泛使用的线性涡黏模型中评价性能最好一个……它巧妙结合了 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

 和 JK 模型的优点。除了具有上述 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

 的稳定性好、精度高等优点外，还可以较好地处理湍流剪切应力在逆压梯度和分离边界层内的输运，故 SST 模型能更好地预测逆压梯度和边界层分离等较复杂的流动情况。因
此，SST 模型以其精度高、鲁棒性好、适用性较广而成为航空航 天领域应用最广的湍流模型之一。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
SST (Shear Stress Transport) 模型由 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Menter_1994"
literal "false"

\end_inset

 通过在内层（近壁区）采用 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

 模型、在外层（边界层边缘、自由剪切层）采用（变换为 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

 形式的）高雷诺数 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

 模型而得到 。形式上，该模型仍需求解 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

 模型的两个方程：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\frac{\partial\rho k}{\partial t}+\frac{\partial\rho u_{j}k}{\partial x_{j}} & =\frac{\partial}{\partial x_{j}}\left[\left(\mu_{L}+\sigma_{k}\,\mu_{T}\right)\frac{\partial k}{\partial x_{j}}\right]+\tau_{ij}^{F}\,S_{ij}-\beta^{*}\,\rho\,\omega\,k,\\
\frac{\partial\rho\omega}{\partial t}+\frac{\partial\rho u_{j}\omega}{\partial x_{j}} & =\frac{\partial}{\partial x_{j}}\left[\left(\mu_{L}+\sigma_{\omega}\,\mu_{T}\right)\frac{\partial\omega}{\partial x_{j}}\right]+\tau_{ij}^{F}\,S_{ij}\,C_{\omega}\,\rho\,\mu_{T}^{-1}-\beta\,\rho\,\omega^{2}+(1-f_{1})\frac{2\rho\,\sigma_{\omega2}}{\omega}\frac{\partial k}{\partial x_{j}}\frac{\partial\omega}{\partial x_{j}},
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\beta^{*}=0.09$
\end_inset

，函数 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{1}$
\end_inset

 用于混合内层系数 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{1}$
\end_inset

 与外层系数 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{2}$
\end_inset

 ：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{1}=\tanh(\min\left[\max\left\{ \frac{\sqrt{k}}{0.09\,\omega\,d},\frac{500\,\mu_{L}}{\rho\,\omega\,d^{2}}\right\} ,\frac{4\rho\sigma_{\omega2}k}{\mathrm{CD}_{k\omega}\,d^{2}}\right]),
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{CD}_{k\omega}$
\end_inset

 为交叉耗散项中的正项，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{CD}_{k\omega}=\max\left(\frac{2\rho\,\sigma_{\omega2}}{\omega}\frac{\partial k}{\partial x_{j}}\frac{\partial\omega}{\partial x_{j}},10^{-20}\right),
\]

\end_inset

混合后的系数为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\phi=f_{1}\phi_{1}+(1-f_{1})\,\phi_{2},
\]

\end_inset

内部 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

 模型系数为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma_{k}=0.85,\quad\sigma_{\omega}=0.5,\quad\beta=0.075,\quad C_{\omega}=0.533,
\]

\end_inset

外部 
\begin_inset Formula $k$
\end_inset

–
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon$
\end_inset

 模型系数为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma_{k}=1.0,\quad\sigma_{\omega}=0.856,\quad\beta=0.0828,\quad C_{\omega}=0.44,
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
湍流黏度为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mu_{T}=\frac{a_{1}\,\rho\,k}{\max(a_{1}\,\omega,f_{2}\norm{\curl\vec{u}})}\leftarrow a_{1}=0.31,
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{2}=\tanh(\left(\max\left[\frac{2\sqrt{k}}{0.09\,\omega\,d},\frac{500\,\mu_{L}}{\rho\,\omega\,d^{2}}\right]\right)^{2}),
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

